all the wine at home.

433
00:41:38,400 --> 00:41:39,220
Dad.

434
00:41:39,660 --> 00:41:41,310
Isn't this wine?

435
00:41:42,840 --> 00:41:44,800
Just go ahead and drink it.

436
00:41:46,370 --> 00:41:49,550
