439
00:41:59,640 --> 00:42:00,330
Me?

440
00:42:03,400 --> 00:42:04,640
First.

441
00:42:05,170 --> 00:42:06,330
I'm handsome.

442
00:42:06,330 --> 00:42:07,260
Okay.

443
00:42:08,440 --> 00:42:10,020
I'm handsome.

444
00:42:10,020 --> 00:42:10,840
Okay.

445
00:42:11,770 --> 00:42:14,440
I can make people happy.

446
00:42:19,660 --> 00:42:20,350
Right.

447
00:42:21,530 --> 00:42:24,060
I'm good at dancing.

448
00:42:24,640 --> 00:42:26,020
Was it during the opening ceremony?

449
00:42:26,350 --> 00:42:27,680
Well, during that time,

450
00:42:27,680 --> 00:42:30,530
