516
00:49:44,680 --> 00:49:45,860
Get out from here now.

517
00:49:45,860 --> 00:49:47,310
He made a fuss!

518
00:49:47,310 --> 00:49:48,820
Yi Na, don't listen to her.

519
00:49:49,350 --> 00:49:51,480
