This can't be.

554
00:51:35,040 --> 00:51:37,440
I said, please take it up!

555
00:51:37,440 --> 00:51:38,400
Goodness!

556
00:51:58,930 --> 00:52:00,080
No way.

557
00:52:14,950 --> 00:52:16,970
Congratulations!

558
00:52:16,970 --> 00:52:18,950
Thank you!

559
00:52:41,170 --> 00:52:42,130
I'll count to three.

560
00:52:42,130 --> 00:52:42,710
Okay.

561
00:52:43,200 --> 00:52:45,400
1, 2, 3.

562
00:52:47,370 --> 00:52:48,660
One more.

563
00:52:50,640 --> 00:52:52,930
1, 2, 3.

564
00:53:04,600 --> 00:53:06,170
It's over.

565
00:53:07,280 --> 00:53:08,860
Let's go.

566
00:53:08,860 --> 00:53:09,820
How nice.

567
00:53:09,820 --> 00:53:10,510
Let's go.

568
00:53:11,550 --> 00:53:12,860
Bye-bye.

569
00:53:25,330 --> 00:53:26,820
Wait a minute.

570
00:53:26,820 --> 00:53:28,040
Just for a bit.

571
00:53:47,550 --> 00:53:49,420
Oh my.

572
00:53:54,150 --> 00:53:57,000
I will miss you, Mom and Dad.

573
00:53:57,330 --> 00:53:58,370
Enjoy your trip.

574
00:53:58,370 --> 00:53:59,400
I got it.

575
00:53:59,420 --> 00:54:00,370
I love you.

576
00:54:00,370 --> 00:54:01,530
I love you all too.

577
00:54:01,970 --> 00:54:03,730
I'll call you later, Dad. Okay?

578
00:54:03,730 --> 00:54:04,480
Just go.

579
00:54:04,480 --> 00:54:05,620
Don't cry.

580
00:54:06,460 --> 00:54:07,480
We're leaving.

581
00:56:40,370 --> 00:56:41,880
Just go now.

582
00:57:21,840 --> 00:57:23,550
Oh, I heard you got married.

583
00:57:23,550 --> 00:57:24,480
Congrats.

584
00:57:24,480 --> 00:57:26,480
Oh, hello.

585
00:57:28,620 --> 00:57:30,330
Otherwise, I'll re-send it to you.

586
00:57:30,660 --> 00:57:33,200
Please send me a text message
of your e-mail address.

587
00:57:40,330 --> 00:57:41,130
Hello there.

588
00:57:41,130 --> 00:57:42,170
Hi!

589
00:57:42,170 --> 00:57:43,000
Oh.

590
00:58:02,280 --> 00:58:03,310
Senior.

591
00:58:03,970 --> 00:58:05,620
I sent it through e-mail.

592
00:58:08,000 --> 00:58:09,060
Where did you go?

593
00:58:09,060 --> 00:58:10,350
I went to my school.

594
00:58:10,350 --> 00:58:11,860
Really? Have you eaten yet?

595
00:58:11,860 --> 00:58:14,400
Goodness. I'm sick of it every time we meet.

596
00:58:14,400 --> 00:58:16,350
Basically, you're like being possessed by cats.

597
00:58:22,350 --> 00:58:23,640
Okay, cheers.

598
00:58:24,310 --> 00:58:24,880
Hey.

599
00:58:25,170 --> 00:58:26,150
Let's have a drink.

600
00:58:26,150 --> 00:58:27,600
Come on, let's have a drink.

601
00:58:27,600 --> 00:58:28,530
Cheers.

602
00:58:28,530 --> 00:58:30,530
Cheers!

603
00:58:33,820 --> 00:58:35,370
You're showing off here.

604
00:58:39,040 --> 00:58:41,040
Damn you. You already own a clothing store?

605
00:58:44,240 --> 00:58:47,600
[ 2 years later ]

606
00:59:18,420 --> 00:59:19,040
What's this?

607
00:59:19,480 --> 00:59:22,530
1003. The door is now open.

608
00:59:48,550 --> 00:59:49,880
This is Jung Woo.

609
00:59:56,770 --> 00:59:58,000
Father-in-law!

610
00:59:58,570 --> 01:00:00,480
I know you're all there!

611
01:00:23,530 --> 01:00:24,860
Father-in-law!

612
01:00:25,530 --> 01:00:26,800
Mother-in-law!

613
